ille]]<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" /><br />[[Susie Shinner]]{{ref|young|Y}}(deleted scene)<br />[[Ellie Darcey-Alden|Ellie Darcey-Alden]]{{ref|young|Y}}\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Annabel Baldwin<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Lauren Nicole Cipoletti\n|-\n! [[List of supporting Harry Potter characters#Lily Potter|Lily Potter Jr]]\n| Daphne de Beistegui<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Zoe Brough<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" /><br />Cristina Fray<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" /><br />Christiana Hutchings<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Olivia Bond<br />[[Brooklyn Shuck]]\n|-\n! [[Newt Scamander]]\n| {{N/A|''Appearance in print''}}{{efn|name=Scamander|Newt Scamander's name appeared on the [[Marauder's Map]] in the ''Prisoner of Azkaban'' film.<ref name=\"ScamanderMarauderMap\" />}}\n| [[Eddie Redmayne]]<ref name=\"RedmayneCast\" /><br />Joshua Shea{{ref|young|Y}}<ref name=\"Shea\" />\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n! [[Severus Snape]]\n| [[Alan Rickman]]<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" /><br />Alec Hopkins{{ref|young|Y}}<br />Benedict Clarke{{ref|young|Y}}\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Paul Bentall<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Byron Jennings<ref name=\"MeisleHylandJennings\" />\n|-\n! [[Magical objects in Harry Potter#Sorting Hat|Sorting Hat]]\n| [[Leslie Phillips]]{{ref|Voice|V}}<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| [[Chris Jarman]]<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Brian Abraham<ref name=\"AbrahamLouisCipoletti\" />\n|-\n! [[Ministry of Magic#Dolores Umbridge|Dolores Umbridge]]\n| [[Imelda Staunton]]<ref name=\"Staunton\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Helena Lymbery<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Kathryn Meisle<ref name=\"MeisleHylandJennings\" />\n|-\n! [[Lord Voldemort|Lord Voldemort<br /><small>Tom Marvolo Riddle</small>]]\n| [[Ian Hart]]{{ref|voice|V}}{{efn|name=Voldemort|[[Ian Hart]], who played [[Hogwarts staff#Quirinus Quirrell|Quirinus Quirrell]], provided the voice and [[motion capture]] for Voldemort in the ''Philosopher's Stone'' fi