ws)<ref name=\"MChp7\">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-i |title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part I (2010): Reviews |website=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=14 November 2018 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101119054859/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-i |archivedate=19 November 2010 }}</ref>\n| A<ref name=\"HPcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2''\n| 96% (329 reviews)<ref name=\"RThp8\">{{cite web|title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows \u2013 Part 2 (2011) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_deathly_hallows_part_2_2011/ |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=November 1, 2019 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709200351/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_deathly_hallows_part_2_2011/ |archivedate=9 July 2016 }}</ref>\n| 87 (41 reviews)<ref name=\"MChp8\">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2 |title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2 (2011): Reviews |website=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=14 November 2018 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718094558/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2 |archivedate=18 July 2011 }}</ref>\n| A<ref name=\"HPcs\" />\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#ccccff;\" | ''Fantastic Beasts'' films\n|-\n| ''Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them''\n| 74% (333 reviews)<ref name=\"RTfb1\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_beasts_and_where_to_find_them |title=Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them (2016) |website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=November 1, 2019 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606012241/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_beasts_and_where_to_find_them |archivedate=6 June 2017 }}</ref>\n| 66 (50 reviews)<ref 