ame=PercivalGraves|[[Colin Farrell]] portrays Gellert Grindelwald disguised as Percival Graves in ''Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them'', with [[Johnny Depp]] briefly portraying the character in the film without his disguise.<ref name=\"FarrellGrindelwald\" />}}<br />[[Johnny Depp]]<ref name=\"Depp\" /><br />Jamie Campbell Bower{{ref|young|Y}}<ref name=\"RegboBowerFB2\" />\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n! [[Rubeus Hagrid]]\n| [[Robbie Coltrane]]<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" /><br />[[Martin Bayfield]]{{ref|young|Y}}\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| [[Chris Jarman]]<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Brian Abraham\n|-\n! [[List of supporting Harry Potter characters#Viktor Krum|Viktor Krum]]\n| [[Stanislav Ianevski]]<ref name=\"GoFFullCast\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Jack North<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Joey LaBrasca\n|-\n! [[Draco Malfoy]]\n| [[Tom Felton]]<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Alex Price]]<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" /><ref name=\"CCBroadwayCast\" />\n|-\n! [[Hogwarts staff#Minerva McGonagall|Minerva McGonagall]]\n| [[Maggie Smith]]<ref name=\"DH2FullCast\" />\n| [[Fiona Glascott]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Moore|first=Sam|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/11/05/professor-mcgonagalls-introduction-in-fantastic-beasts-2-will-break-harry-potter-canon-8105219|title=Professor McGonagall\u2019s introduction in Fantastic Beasts 2 will break Harry Potter canon|work=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro]]|date=5 November 2018|accessdate=18 November 2018}}</ref>\n| Sandy McDade<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| [[Geraldine Hughes]]\n|-\n! [[List of supporting Harry Potter characters#Moaning Myrtle|Moaning Myrtle]]\n| [[Shirley Henderson]]<ref name=\"GoFFullCast\" />\n| {{cEmpty}}\n| Annabel Baldwin<ref name=\"CursedChildFullCast\" />\n| Lauren Nicole Cipoletti<ref name=\"AbrahamLouisCipoletti\" />\n|-\n! [[Magical creatures in Harry Potter#Nagini|Nagini]]\n| {{N/A|''[[Computer-generated imagery|CGI]]''}}\n| [[Claudia Kim]]<ref name=\"Kim\" /