 universe of Harry Potter]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<!-- HARRY POTTER SERIES-->\n\n<ref name=\"Columbus\">{{cite web|url=https://uk.ign.com/articles/2000/03/28/chris-columbus-to-direct-harry-potter|title=Chris Columbus to Direct Harry Potter|last=Linder|first=Bran|date=28 March 2000|website=[[IGN]]|accessdate=8 July 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414061257/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2000/03/28/chris-columbus-to-direct-harry-potter |archivedate=14 April 2016 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Columbus2\">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2465000/2465225.stm |title=Chris Columbus COS: full interview |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |date=13 November 2002 |accessdate=10 October 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070129132824/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2465000/2465225.stm |archivedate=29 January 2007 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kloves\">{{cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/uncategorized/countdown-to-harry-potter-and-the-half-blood-prince-steve-kloves-talks-up-the-final-moments-between/ |title='Harry Potter' countdown: Steve Kloves on a 'haunting moment' in 'Half-Blood Prince' |last=Martin |first=Denise |newspaper=[[Los Angeles Times]] |date=17 June 2009 |accessdate=14 January 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119151407/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/uncategorized/countdown-to-harry-potter-and-the-half-blood-prince-steve-kloves-talks-up-the-final-moments-between/ |archivedate=19 January 2016 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Cuaron\">{{cite news|url=https://ew.com/article/2002/07/22/harry-potter-gets-new-director/ |title=''Harry Potter'' gets a new director |last=Susman |first=Gary |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=22 July 2002 |accessdate=10 October 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123043416/http://www.ew.com/article/2002/07/22/harry-potter-gets-new-director |archivedate=23 November 2